{"tid":123491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警判刑】各被告判囚兩年","createTime":"2017-02-17T02:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T03:43:24.000Z","uid":48093,"like":188,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"682f733a86ee73256cbd5760e2bbedab691db855","tid":123491,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487291386_4d39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487291386_4d39.jpg&h=f1bdef02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7名警員於佔領期間在添馬公園變電站暗角位置，毆打公民黨前成員曾健超，7人於周二被裁定襲擊致他人受傷罪成，第五被告則因於警署掌摑曾健超而另被裁定普通襲擊罪成。法官今判刑時指斥各被告損香港聲譽，特別是全球也有很多人看到，即使曾健超是犯法、警方有壓力，但亦不可帶他往暗角打，故判囚是適合的。法官以入獄兩年半為量刑起點，判囚兩年。<br />\n7名被告依序為有組織罪案及三合會調查科總督察黃祖成（49歲）、觀塘區反黑組高級督察劉卓毅（30歲）、觀塘區反黑組警長白榮斌（43歲）、觀塘區反黑 組警員劉興沛（39歲）、東九龍總區刑事總部警員陳少丹（32歲）、九龍城區刑事偵緝警員關嘉豪（33歲）及觀塘區反黑組警員黃偉豪（37歲）。"},{"pid":"bf530c3e4f8e7adb2a56cc4f3de7d8ee78a42440","tid":123491,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cd5b34193901fdedb5050188bcb72c6c36e235","tid":123491,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdd985a52fbf4d0395685f7c491a3513cb58aef","tid":123491,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb164fff93c406081d2f472bb66eb92491b2aaaf","tid":123491,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji